description:
Replicate data from cloud applications such as Freshdesk, Exact Online, Visma Severa, Nmbrs and over 70 other platforms into a relational database such as Microsoft SQL Server or PostgreSQL.

Invantive Data Loader allows you to replicate data from cloud applications such as Freshdesk, Exact Online, Visma Severa, Nmbrs and over 70 other platforms in a relational database such as Microsoft SQL Server or PostgreSQL.
